{"tid":1084841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥吧絲！每日只食1000kcal","createTime":"2019-03-30T16:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T05:52:30.000Z","uid":171337,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4d5ccc907c1d2361684296563872f6925ca948","tid":1084841,"uid":171337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"冬天過後，相信好多絲打都開始搵緊減肥（極速）方法。美孚小修女決心不再做肥婆，要減肥！仲要每日做30分鐘運動同埋每日只食1000Kcal。希望做到極速減肥之餘唔反彈。<br />\n<br />\n修女重災區係下半身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，肉感肥大髀肉加埋粗壯肌肉小腿，真係唔敢着短褲....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />修女返一份Office工令到肚腩仔變左個大肚腩，真係好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要立刻趕住喺夏天嚟之前減個靚肥，依家同大家分享下我既獨門秘技。<br />\n<br />\n飲食<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道有一條formula可以計到你每日需要食幾多卡路里（靜止狀態完全唔郁）：<br />\n<br />\n女: BMR = 655 + ( 9.6 x 體重kg ) + ( 1.8 x 身高cm ) - ( 4.7 x 年齡years )<br />\n男: BMR = 66 + ( 13.7 x 體重kg ) + ( 5 x 身高cm ) - ( 6.8 x 年齡years ）<br />\n<br />\n修女每日要食約1200kcal,為咗達到減肥效果決定每日只食1000！餐單如下：<br />\n<br />\n早：latte 200kcal, 香蕉85kcal<br />\n午餐：同同事食，盡量減少份量(約500kcal)<br />\n晚餐：獨特的K減肥麥片131kcal，脫脂奶一盒85kcal<br />\n其實盡量食健康d，留意返自己有冇食過量就可以，唔需要日日跟著食同樣既野。<br />\n<br />\n運動<br />\n<br />\n修女心肺功能比較差，行兩步都喘晒氣，亦完全唔係好動既朋友。所以跟YouTube片係屋企做，其實每日做30分鐘都已經熱到出晒汗。我鍾意一啲會減到肥而且改善肌肉線條嘅exercises，想推介呢類片俾大家，你地都可以搵一啲改善埋肌肉線條嘅片嚟跟住做。<a href=\"https://youtu.be/A5K-ioB5o6A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FA5K-ioB5o6A&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6lLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=fab71f9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/A5K-ioB5o6A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不反彈<br />\n<br />\n減左幾星期之後應該會有成果，要唔返彈就要keep住健康既飲食習慣，例如每餐食7成飽同埋多做運動等等講到口臭既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家都有個自己滿意既身型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5d2e6fe84322176e56f06dc48f26482e7a0890","tid":1084841,"uid":16968,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"1000 卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3f38c5e305dfecff95f6c5aae8458e064f350c","tid":1084841,"uid":141892,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"每日要2000KCAL"},{"pid":"048fdd52461e40326c05bd27a67a4cf8b3f6f55e","tid":1084841,"uid":21757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:16:30.000Z","msg":"原來只需要1146 kcal 每天"},{"pid":"79ac67814f8cb1360323fb6d3bb1db04baf6fb95","tid":1084841,"uid":192401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T21:28:21.000Z","msg":"早餐唔飲野淨食麥皮<br />\n午餐晚餐都可以食豐富啲"},{"pid":"37c9cd527b8f0f38a058e12633be5f3e2e95d57a","tid":1084841,"uid":71508,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T23:34:56.000Z","msg":"1000 kcal<br />\n你等反彈肥返la"},{"pid":"33500939ea6c88796a2268a8e1e1a9cdb24709a5","tid":1084841,"uid":29689,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"減肥唔係要高過bmr 低過 tdee 咩<br />\n低過bmr 會減慢新陳代謝<br />\n幾肯定會反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe8f6193579b252491bfd3f2405ea1c0caac9b1","tid":1084841,"uid":19004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"latte 轉齋啡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d86c07098d9f192c4b6c1cf6a755aee2e4002a2","tid":1084841,"uid":20302,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"女人減肥真係唔用腦<br />\n<br />\n減肥都蠢過人 <br />\n<br />\n上網搵下咩叫tdee先啦 <br />\n<br />\n一千卡 笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766b4b959a9f7c690c74b63ccb156ecce81e0e45","tid":1084841,"uid":51717,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"原來仲有on9每日只食1000卡去減肥"},{"pid":"146a479a83af8350631a27fd04e270ab32c7dfde","tid":1084841,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"